00:53:24.589 --> 00:53:27.506
I'm hoping for two things from you.

00:53:28.690 --> 00:53:29.876
I'm an East Coast transplant.

00:53:29.876 --> 00:53:31.226
I'm from Philadelphia.

00:53:31.226 --> 00:53:33.043
Lived there for, grew up there.

00:53:33.043 --> 00:53:36.082
Came out to California about 30 years ago.

00:53:36.082 --> 00:53:39.628
And I still have trouble
communicating with Californians.

00:53:39.628 --> 00:53:42.415
(audience laughing)

00:53:42.415 --> 00:53:44.998
- Now I have to interrupt here,

00:53:45.842 --> 00:53:47.827
because I'm from Brooklyn,
